('any', 'ukraine', 'Investor', 'Temporary Residence Permit (Investor)',
 '⚠️ Investment in Ukraine carries extreme risk due to the ongoing conflict. Post-war reconstruction may create significant investment opportunities. Ukraine''s government has indicated plans for post-war international investment frameworks.',
