('any', 'ukraine', 'Family', 'Temporary Residence Permit (Family of Ukrainian Citizen)',
 'Foreign nationals who are spouses, children, or parents of Ukrainian citizens can obtain a Temporary Residence Permit for family reunification. Under current conflict conditions, many Ukrainian citizens are abroad.',
