 'Enrollment letter from Moroccan institution, financial proof, valid passport, criminal record, medical certificate.',
 'Typically 4–8 weeks', 'MAD 300–700',
 'study', '4–8 weeks', 'Duration of studies, renewable', CURRENT_DATE),

('any', 'morocco', 'Digital Nomad', 'Morocco Digital Nomad Initiative / Long-Stay Visa',
